\v 3 Zvatakanzwa nezvatakaziva, Nezvatakaudzwa namadzibaba edu.
\v 4 Hatingazvivanziri vana vavo, Asi tichaudza rudzi runotevera mabwa uvgulittdm aikkffikva, Nesimba rake, namabasa ake, anoshamisa, aakaita.
\v 5 Nokuti akamutsa chipupuriro pakati. paJakobho, Akatema murayiro pakati paIsiraeri, Akazviraira madzibaba edu, Kuti vazvizivise vana vavo;
\v 6 Kuti rudzi runotevera ruzvizive, ivo vana vachazoberekwa; Ivo vasimuke vazviudze vana vavo;
\v 7 Kuti tariro yavo ive kuna Mwari, Varege kukanganwa mabasa aMwari, Asi vachengete mirairo yake;
\v 8 Varege kufanana namadzibaba avo, Rwakanga ruri rudzi rusingateereri, rwakamukira Mwari. Rudzi rwakaramba kururamisa mwoyo yavo, Uye mweya yavo yakanga isinakutendeka kuna Mwari.
